https://wiki.apache.org/nutch/NutchTutorial#A4._Setup_Solr_for_search

A slight modification is: They ask us to add the following line:
<field name="content" type="text" stored="true" indexed="true"/>

But type="text" doesn't work. Make it is as "text_general". Then run bin/nutch solrindex yadi-yada...
